'''''The Midnight Mauler''''', a [[Pathfinder Society Roleplaying Guild]] scenario for tier 1-7 by [[Crystal Frasier]], was released in January 2011 as an exclusive scenario, and in February 2012 for general play.

{{Quote
| quote  = The [[Decemvirate]] sends members of the [[Pathfinder Society]] to the former crown jewel of [[Ustalav|Ustalav's]] royal courts, the decaying city of [[Ardis]]. Tasked by the Society to look into the fate of [[Absalom|Absalom's]] former [[Master of Blades]], [[Vonran Vilk]], what they find will lead to exploration, diplomacy, murder, haunted pasts, and tragic love. Can the PCs stop the rampage of the Midnight Mauler before he kills again?
}}

